OL,6,FWhen she opened the container, parish
OL,7,Fminister Rev Dr MaryAnn Rennie found
OL,8,Fthe pieces wrapped in a copy of the
OL,9,FFife and Kinross Extra newspaper,
OL,10,Fdated February 12 2005, and
OL,11,Faccompanied by an anonymous
OL,12,Ftypewritten note.
OL,14,FThe note read: "Hello there, I am
OL,15,Freturning some stained glass that I
OL,16,Ffound over 20 years ago. It was in a
OL,17,Fsmall pile below the scaffold that was
OL,18,Ferected by the Abbey (near footpath
OL,19,Ffacing west.)
