OL,6,F"I wrapped it up in paper to protect
OL,7,Fit but never had the chance to return
OL,8,Fit. Unsure if was new glass going in
OL,9,For old coming out.
OL,11,F"I felt a bit guilty taking it and
OL,12,Fhope it will get used. Regards, CEEPS".
OL,14,FThe minister and congregation were
OL,15,Fmystified as they were not able to
OL,16,Fwork out which of the 10 fully intact
OL,17,Fstained-glass windows in the Abbey
OL,18,FChurch the pieces originally belonged
OL,19,Fto.
