OL,3,CExperts solve mystery of glass window
OL,4,Cshards anonymously returned to abbey
OL,6,FHowever academic experts have now
OL,7,Fsolved the mystery, using a
OL,8,Fcombination of science, history and
OL,9,Fvisual analysis, and have established
OL,10,Fthat the fragments and shards were
OL,11,Foriginally part of the Margaret Window.
OL,13,FDating from 1932 and designed by
OL,14,FAlexander Strachan, it shows the
OL,15,Fmarriage of Queen Margaret and King
OL,16,FMalcolm Canmore.
