OL,3,CExperts solve mystery of glass window
OL,4,Cshards anonymously returned to abbey
OL,6,FDr Rennie turned to Professor Michael
OL,7,FPenman, Professor of History at the
OL,8,FUniversity of Stirling, for help in
OL,9,F2023, after appeals for information on
OL,10,Fsocial media proved fruitless.
OL,12,FProfessor Penman looked at old Kirk
OL,13,FSession records dating back to the
OL,14,Fearly 1980s to work out when damage
OL,15,Fwas caused to stained glass windows at
OL,16,Fthe Abbey Church or when repairs were
OL,17,Fmade.
