OL,3,CExperts solve mystery of glass window
OL,4,Cshards anonymously returned to abbey
OL,6,FHe also enlisted the help of his
OL,7,Ffriend, scientist Dr Craig Kennedy of
OL,8,Fthe Institute for Sustainable Building
OL,9,FDesign at Heriot-Watt University in
OL,10,FEdinburgh.
OL,12,FDr Kennedy tested the shards and
OL,13,Ffragments using the university's
OL,14,Felectron microscopy facility and x-ray
OL,15,Ffluorescence to identify the elements
OL,16,Fpresent, which in turn revealed the
OL,17,Fcolour of the glass and where it came
OL,18,Ffrom.
