OL,3,CExperts solve mystery of glass window
OL,4,Cshards anonymously returned to abbey
OL,6,FShe determined that they depicted an
OL,7,Fangel's wing, the knotwork hem of a
OL,8,Fnoble's robe, the hair of an angel and
OL,9,Fa thistle motif that was repeatedly
OL,10,Fused in a window design.
OL,12,FMs Kelly visited the Abbey Church,
OL,13,Fbuilt in 1821 in the Fife town, and
OL,14,Feventually worked out that the stained-
OL,15,Fglass pieces were originally part of
OL,16,Fthe Margaret Window in the south
OL,17,Ftransept.
