OL,3,CExperts solve mystery of glass window
OL,4,Cshards anonymously returned to abbey
OL,6,FShe could see where the glass had been
OL,7,Freplaced as the colour and texture of
OL,8,Fthe material used was slightly
OL,9,Fdifferent to the original pieces.
OL,11,FDr Rennie said: "We are delighted that
OL,12,Fthe mystery of where this glass
OL,13,Foriginally came from has finally been
OL,14,Funravelled.
OL,16,F"We still have no idea who CEEPS is
OL,17,Fand why they decided to return it to
OL,18,Fthe abbey when they did, but we are
OL,19,Fgrateful."
