OL,3,CExperts solve mystery of glass window
OL,4,Cshards anonymously returned to abbey
OL,6,FMs Kelly said her "best guess" is the
OL,7,FMargaret Window was struck and damaged
OL,8,Fby a scaffolding pole during
OL,9,Frefurbishment work in the late 1990s.
OL,11,FShe added: "But unless CEEPS comes
OL,12,Fforward, the full circumstances behind
OL,13,Fthe disappearance and reappearance of
OL,14,Fthe glass will remain an intriguing
OL,15,Fpart of the abbey's history."
OL,17,FMeanwhile, the name "Bob Brewse" is
OL,18,Funderstood to be a playful reference
OL,19,Fto King Robert the Bruce, whose
OL,20,Fremains are interred in the church.
