OL,6,FThe Abbey Church is facing a repair
OL,7,Fbill of around #4 million to ensure it
OL,8,Fremains wind and watertight and a
OL,9,Ffurther #4 million to upgrade its
OL,10,Ffacilities, and has launched a
OL,11,Ffundraising appeal.
OL,13,FThe four large stained glass pieces
OL,14,Fwill be on display at an exhibition
OL,15,Fexamining the role of the church in
OL,16,Fthe local community and its history,
OL,17,Fwhich opens at Dunfermline Carnegie
OL,18,FLibrary and Galleries on March 22 and
OL,19,Fruns until April 6.
